DTEND:20260317T171000Z
SUMMARY:Attract and retain
DESCRIPTION:Exploring strategies to attract talent and companies to the Monterrey ecosystem\, while keeping in mind the importance of retaining and empowering local talent and entrepreneurship as the foundation of a solid and sustainable innovation district.\n\nSpeakers: Juan Bringas\, Pamela Cedeño\, Jessy Fonseca\, Aquino Eloah
