UID:aee56dd0-6010-4f8c-a23a-ab58e4535cac@incmty2026
DTSTART:20260317T163000Z
DTEND:20260317T171000Z
SUMMARY:Foreign Investment and Talent Mobility
DESCRIPTION:It is a conversation between Fernando Mayer\, Director General of Foreign Investment at the Ministry of Economy\, and César Becker\, an expert on migration and talent mobility issues. They will analyze Mexico's strengths\, touching on topics such as official FDI figures\, Mexico's negotiation capabilities\, and what corporate migration means in promoting investment in Mexico.\n\nSpeakers: César Becker\, Fernando Mayer
LOCATION:TEC | INSPIRE STAGE | (RECTORIA - SALA MAYOR)
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:5966b762-518b-474a-9a2a-66aa1d8e9bd2@incmty2026
DTSTART:20260317T163000Z
DTEND:20260317T171000Z
SUMMARY:The New Frontier of Investment
DESCRIPTION:This panel brings together national leaders to explore mobilizing capital for STEM startups capable of transforming industries\, redefining markets\, and monetizing innovation. Beyond traditional financing\, we will explore mechanisms for building robust investment ecosystems. During the panel\, we will discuss how to strengthen trust between researchers and investors and how to design regulatory frameworks and financial instruments that drive the transition to a knowledge economy.\n\nSpeakers: César Aspiros\, Pedro Lopez Sela\, Rogelio Marín\, Alejandra Vazquez
LOCATION:TEC | CREATE WORKSHOPS | (BIBLIOTECA - SALA POEMA & DIALOGO)
END:VEVENT
