DESCRIPTION:Tour of the areas where students build prototypes and experiment with different materials.\n\nSpeakers: Escuela de Arquitectura\, Arte y Diseño (EAAD)
LOCATION:TEC | Aulas 4 - 129-1
END:VEVENT
