UID:63fd88d6-0c8c-4747-8d0d-0bd6446bc0bb@incmty2026
DTSTART:20260317T165000Z
DTEND:20260317T171000Z
SUMMARY:How to create new businesses without disrupting operations
DESCRIPTION:Good ideas don't fail: they get bogged down in the execution.The problem isn't innovation\, it's the method. This talk introduces VentureMode™\, an entrepreneurial way to run new businesses without letting the system dilute them.\n\nSpeakers: Camilo Manjarrés
LOCATION:TEC | INNOVATION WORKSHOP | (EXPEDITION FEMSA - SALA POLIVALENTE)
END:VEVENT
