SUMMARY:CASA EXATEC: Maximize Your EXATEC Benefits
DESCRIPTION:EXATEC Exclusive: A personalized assistance space to learn about our network of partnerships. Resolve specific questions and discover how to make the most of the discounts in your daily life.\n\nSpeakers: CASA EXATEC
