SUMMARY:Hit Play on Your Idea
DESCRIPTION:Talk on topics such as public policy\, entrepreneurship\, innovation\, and business\, structured into six thematic blocks. Each block will include moments of interaction with the audience to maintain active participation from the speakers and encourage the generation of organic content. At the end\, a Q&A session will be opened to further explore the topics discussed and promote dialogue with the audience.\n\nSpeakers: Virginia Hernández Vázquez\, Fito De La Isla
