SUMMARY:Keys to improving productivity
DESCRIPTION:Simon Cohen\, one of Mexico's most admired entrepreneurs and a "shark" on Shark Tank\, reveals that true productivity stems not from exhausting effort\, but from strategic clarity and personal well-being. In this session\, Simon shares the practical tools that led him to found one of the world's most successful logistics companies\, demonstrating how process optimization and people-centered leadership can radically transform the results of any business.\n\nSpeakers: Simon Cohen
LOCATION:TEC | TELCEL 5G STAGE | (CENTRO DE CONGRESOS - SALA 1 Y 2)
END:VEVENT
