DTEND:20260317T224000Z
SUMMARY:Grow Your Business with AI
DESCRIPTION:The "Grow Your Business with AI" workshop\, based on the book "Hack Your Business\," is an intensive workshop for business owners in Mexico seeking exponential growth. The goal is to share the latest trending tools in a practical way to transform your business in three months\, focusing on increasing sales\, improving efficiency\, and enhancing the customer experience. The core content is the practical and correct use of Artificial Intelligence tools to boost productivity and creativity. The workshop concludes with the creation of a 100-day plan for implementation and achieving results.\n\nSpeakers: Jahasiel E. Sevilla Muñoz
LOCATION:TEC | INNOVATION WORKSHOP | (EXPEDITION FEMSA - SALA POLIVALENTE)
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:c9d15807-b0b7-40c0-a4d1-80dab0bda7c9@incmty2026
DTSTART:20260317T214000Z
DTEND:20260317T222000Z
SUMMARY:Panel: Silicon Valley & Mexico: AI\, Venture Capital and the Future of Global Innovation
DESCRIPTION:Silicon Valley remains the global epicenter of technological innovation\, venture capital\, and the development of artificial intelligence. At the same time\, Mexico is emerging as a strategic partner in talent\, entrepreneurship\, and the scaling of technology companies across the Americas. This panel brings together leaders from the Silicon Valley ecosystem and cross-border innovation networks to explore how AI\, venture capital\, and international collaboration are shaping the next generation of global innovation. The conversation will highlight opportunities for startups\, investors\, and institutions to build stronger bridges between Silicon Valley and Mexico\, accelerating technology development\, investment flows\, and entrepreneurial growth across the region.\n\nSpeakers: Sean Randolph\, Ursula Amanda Rojas Weiser\, Alejandra Martinez
LOCATION:TEC | BOLD VISION | (EXPEDITION FEMSA - AUDITORIO)
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:6b5255c1-1c27-4203-8c45-85a53483ded1@incmty2026
DTSTART:20260317T214000Z
DTEND:20260317T224000Z
SUMMARY:Mastering .MX: How to Turn Your Domain into a Sales Machine with Tiendanube
DESCRIPTION:DescriptionIn this workshop\, we will explore how a domain can become the starting point for building a strong and profitable digital business. Drawing from experience in e-commerce and digital marketing\, you will learn how to leverage your .MX domain to create an online store\, strengthen your brand\, and turn visitors into customers. During the session\, we will share best practices\, tools\, and strategies to launch or scale a digital business using Tiendanube\, including how to connect your domain to an e-commerce platform and optimize your online presence to attract customers and drive growth.ObjectiveTo demonstrate how a .MX domain can become the foundation of a successful digital business by providing participants with practical tools and strategies to create\, position\, and grow their online store using Tiendanube.\n\nSpeakers: Alfredo Huerta
LOCATION:TEC | CREATE WORKSHOPS | (BIBLIOTECA - SALA POEMA & DIALOGO)
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:dbd86707-486f-409c-a8a3-b3beb4ece02c@incmty2026
DTSTART:20260317T214000Z
DTEND:20260317T222000Z
SUMMARY:Powering IA and Digital Transformation with Dell Technologies
DESCRIPTION:AI is the primary force accelerating digital transformation\, and most legacy data centers can’t keep up. A modern data center and multicloud foundation from Dell Technologies enables customers to ride this wave of AI by bringing AI closer to their data\, modernizing application platforms\, and unifying multicloud and edge environments so that AI and other workloads run wherever they generate the greatest value.At the same time\, built-in automation\, efficiency\, security\, and cyber resilience free up budget and human resources to focus on innovation.\n\nSpeakers: Arturo Benavides
LOCATION:TEC | INSPIRE STAGE | (RECTORIA - SALA MAYOR)
END:VEVENT
