DESCRIPTION:Discover the perspectives of women in sports\, business\, and entrepreneurship\n\nSpeakers: Alexia Delgado\, Fernanda Corral\, María Eugenia Pérez\, Silvia Rico
LOCATION:TEC | TELCEL 5G STAGE | (CENTRO DE CONGRESOS - SALA 1 Y 2)
END:VEVENT
