SUMMARY:CASA EXATEC: Turning AI into Your Competitive Advantage
DESCRIPTION:Exclusive for EXATEC: Provide alumni with tools to personalize and utilize artificial intelligence as a strategic ally\, turning it into a competitive advantage for their professional development.\n\nSpeakers: Octavio Edelberto Reyes Torres
