SUMMARY:Staying relevant as an independent creative in an ever changing market
DESCRIPTION:Technology is ever changing and so are we. As a creative of over 35 years in the world of storytelling in animation and live action. I will discuss the importance of embracing change. How to evolve yourself as a creative and continue to stay relevant in a fast changing digital market.\n\nSpeakers: Travis Blaise
