SUMMARY:Attention: The new economy - How to win with content and accelerate with AI
DESCRIPTION:Today\, attention is the most valuable currency. In this talk\, we'll see how to win it through content channels—image\, audio\, voice\, and text—and how artificial intelligence enhances each one to compete with greater impact\, speed\, and scale\, turning attention into a real business advantage.\n\nSpeakers: Rubendario Carrero Barroso
LOCATION:TEC | INNOVATION WORKSHOP | (EXPEDITION FEMSA - SALA POLIVALENTE)
