SUMMARY:2026 Trends in Silicon Valley
DESCRIPTION:Startup Land is shifting fast. AI is reshaping entire industries\, venture capitalists are rewriting their playbooks\, and startup teams are smaller\, faster\, and more capital-efficient than ever. In this talk\, I lay out the top ten trends that every entrepreneur\, innovator\, and investor needs to understand to navigate—and win—in the next era of startups.\n\nSpeakers: Bret Waters
