SUMMARY:Monterrey 2026: This is how we build a World Cup
DESCRIPTION:This panel will address how the 2026 FIFA World Cup Monterrey Organizing Committee is preparing from different perspectives. Through the experience of the project leaders\, initiatives will be shared that seek to maximize the event's impact on the city and demonstrate how a global event can generate value for the community\, businesses\, and future generations beyond football. ⚽\n\nSpeakers: Mayra Ramírez Murillo\, Francisco Rodríguez\, Ivan Pérez\, Cesar Arellano Astorga\, Julio Valdés
