SUMMARY:Accelerate your projects with NVIDIA GeForce RTX Artificial Intelligence
DESCRIPTION:In this conference\, we'll explore how AI powers RTX technologies that are transforming learning and industry\, enabling students to accelerate their workflows across various fields. We'll showcase demos in different applications and explore generative AI tools that optimize education and creativity. Finally\, we'll discuss how RTX technologies enhance gaming\, productivity\, and AI development\, preparing students for the new digital age.\n\nSpeakers: Cuauhtémoc “El Pollo” Escárcega
LOCATION:TEC | TELCEL 5G STAGE | (CENTRO DE CONGRESOS - SALA 1 Y 2)
