DESCRIPTION:To inspire the community through the experience of EXATEC leaders who are taking artificial intelligence from strategy to action\, showing how leadership\, innovation\, and technology combine to transform industries and decision-making in a constantly evolving environment.\n\nSpeakers: Ángela Gómez Aíza\, Carles Abarca de Haro\, Daniela Camberos\, Francisco Lebrija Z.
