SUMMARY:Redefining protection: benefits that empower businesses and their people
DESCRIPTION:Explore how technology\, flexible benefits\, and strategic alliances are transforming protection into a competitive advantage. A renewed vision of insurance that drives well-being\, culture\, and sustainable growth for organizations.\n\nSpeakers: Aitor Echeverría Díaz
