BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:c289aea4-37f0-4409-a762-4f3152f8fa93@incmty2026
DTSTART:20260318T171000Z
DTEND:20260318T175000Z
SUMMARY:Intelligence begins with data
DESCRIPTION:The world runs on data. However\, for years\, the signals were there as noise: isolated fragments\, scattered information\, and difficult to interpret. This session explores how we went from observing disconnected data to reading patterns that transform chaos into intelligence and uncertainty into direction.In an environment where data grows in volume\, velocity\, and diversity—structured and unstructured\, distributed across clouds\, systems\, and geographies—the challenge is no longer obtaining information\, but unifying it with governance\, traceability\, and trust so that it generates real results. The discussion addresses why\, without these foundations\, innovation doesn't scale\, returns diminish\, and risk increases.Based on this premise\, the session presents how a unified platform allows AI to be brought to the data (or data to AI)\, eliminating silos and enabling real-time decision-making. With security as the starting point\, Oracle shows how to transform mission-critical data into a driving force for growth\, efficiency\, and innovation\, preparing organizations for the next wave of artificial intelligence: more complex models\, massive volumes of information\, and continuous\, purposeful action."\n\nSpeakers: Elisa Escalante
LOCATION:TEC | TELCEL 5G STAGE | (CENTRO DE CONGRESOS - SALA 1 Y 2)
END:VEVENT
