SUMMARY:The Art of Fulfilling Dreams
DESCRIPTION:Learn about the life of Mexican illustrator Alex Carrillo\, who talks about how his adventure as an illustrator began\, taking his art to art exhibitions\, animated short films\, and collaborating with high-impact international brands.\n\nSpeakers: Alex Carrillo
LOCATION:TEC | INSPIRE STAGE | (RECTORIA - SALA MAYOR)
