DESCRIPTION:Exclusive for EXATEC: Foster collaboration and development among EXATEC SMEs by providing a space to share knowledge\, resources\, opportunities\, and networks that enable them to grow sustainably and improve their market positioning.\n\nSpeakers: Christian Hernando Salazar Mantilla
