SUMMARY:Build and improve your store with AI on Tiendanube
DESCRIPTION:Having an online store is the first step to selling professionally. But you should know something: customers won't come on their own.In the midst of 2026\, thanks to the growth of AI\, you can improve your brand's presence\, optimize product uploads\, customer service\, and even organic search engine positioning.Find out how to improve your store with the help of Tiendanube and its AI functions.\n\nSpeakers: Alfredo Huerta
