SUMMARY:Let's Speak Our Language: From 'Finance Bro' to Finance for All
DESCRIPTION:Have you ever felt like the investment world doesn't speak your language? It's no coincidence: the system was designed to exclude us.In this talk\, we explore how financial jargon became a barrier and how we embarked on a journey to hack it. From a system designed for the few\, "Bro-talk\," to a clearer\, more human\, and transparent way of investing. That's why Pilou was born: to transform investing into a tool for freedom and empowerment.\n\nSpeakers: Andrea de la Garza
LOCATION:TEC | CREATE WORKSHOPS | (BIBLIOTECA - SALA POEMA & DIALOGO)
