SUMMARY:The 5 stars for your professional development
DESCRIPTION:A dynamic conference on how to take responsibility for our professional development\, aligning our career with a strong sense of shared purpose that stems from our greatest strengths and interests\, and how\, through The Big 3\, we put these to use for others while building and living the life we ​​want to live.\n\nSpeakers: Efraín Mendicuti
