SUMMARY:Purpose
DESCRIPTION:Here and Now: Training AttentionA 25-minute in-person practice\, based on the Healthy Minds program and developed by the Tecmilenio Institute of Purpose and Integral Wellbeing\, that invites you to pause the daily rhythm and train mindfulness through guided breathing exercises and awareness of the present moment.\n\nSpeakers: Epifanio Sánchez
LOCATION:TEC | (ESPACIO DE REFLEXION)
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:db6e9330-56f5-45e9-94db-233dd25a3bb9@incmty2026
DTSTART:20260318T210000Z
DTEND:20260318T212000Z
SUMMARY:Bookmeeting: From consumer to ‘homo experiens’: trends in experience and emotion
DESCRIPTION:In a market where technology and AI are accelerating campaigns\, content\, and automation\, the true differentiator is no longer just data: it's experience. This talk explores the paradigm shift from the "rational consumer" to homo experiens: a conscious\, emotional\, and multidimensional individual who chooses brands based on how they make them feel\, the coherence of their experiences\, and the meaning they construct in every interaction.Based on current trends in experience\, emotion\, and behavior\, the session presents how journeys are evolving (becoming more fragmented and "phygital")\, why emotion has become a strategic asset (memory\, preference\, recommendation)\, and what this means for designing relevant brands: less interruption\, more utility\; less promise\, more proof\; less campaigning\, more consistency. The content culminates in a practical framework for leaders and entrepreneurs to identify "moments of truth" and redesign experiences that generate real differentiation\, trust\, and growth.\n\nSpeakers: Ronan Massez
LOCATION:TEC | (EXPEDITION FEMSA - VENTURE CAFE)
END:VEVENT
