SUMMARY:Digitalize and Sell with AI by Lovable Vibecoding Hackathon
DESCRIPTION:A 2-hour hands-on workshop designed for entrepreneurs\, students\, and small to medium-sized businesses looking to modernize and scale their operations using Artificial Intelligence and e-commerce tools. During the session\, participants will receive an introduction to the world of Lovable and learn how to automate processes\, easily implement e-commerce solutions\, improve sales and operational efficiency\, and use accessible digital tools without the need for advanced technical knowledge. The approach is 100% practical and focused on immediate results.\n\nSpeakers: Fernando Obregon
