SUMMARY:Unwavering Leadership
DESCRIPTION:Unwavering LeadershipIn an environment where innovation moves faster than certainty\, leadership is no longer based solely on strategy\, but on the mental fortitude and human skills of the leader.In this conference\, we will explore how truly unwavering leadership is forged\, not innate. Being a leader today is not just about directing\; it's about remaining calm when everything changes\, making conscious decisions\, and inspiring others to go beyond what they thought possible.Because true leadership emerges when your mind becomes unwavering…and your team perceives it.\n\nSpeakers: Celia Martínez del Toro
LOCATION:TEC | INNOVATION WORKSHOP | (EXPEDITION FEMSA - SALA POLIVALENTE)
END:VEVENT
