DTSTART:20260318T212000Z
DTEND:20260318T220000Z
SUMMARY:Everyone can change the world
DESCRIPTION:In his talk\, "Everyone Can Change the World\," young social entrepreneur Mateo Salvatto guides us through his journey from an average high school student to one of Argentina's most respected tech entrepreneurs.Mateo takes us from laughter to tears\, showing us how his projects (with their successes and failures) can help empower more than 500\,000 people with disabilities worldwide\, and convinces us that changing the world is much easier than we think.\n\nSpeakers: Mateo Salvatto
LOCATION:TEC | TELCEL 5G STAGE | (CENTRO DE CONGRESOS - SALA 1 Y 2)
END:VEVENT
