SUMMARY:CASA EXATEC: The Power of Our Network: Building a Global EXATEC Brand Starts with You.
DESCRIPTION:EXATEC Exclusive. A conversation on the role and responsibility of the EXATEC community in the global positioning of Tecnológico de Monterrey.\n\nSpeakers: Jorge Paz-Soldan
