SUMMARY:Happy Hour by Digital Hub Mty
DESCRIPTION:This space will be a Happy Hour by Digital Hub Mty\, an informal gathering designed to connect corporate leaders\, startups\, and key players from the innovation ecosystem in a relaxed and open environment for conversation. During two hours\, attendees will be able to exchange ideas\, share experiences\, and explore potential collaborations outside the traditional context of formal meetings.The objective of this gathering is to foster genuine connections\, strengthen relationships across ecosystems\, and generate new collaboration opportunities\, all within a comfortable and social setting that encourages participants to enjoy\, converse\, and naturally expand their professional network.The event will take place on March 19 from 6:00 to 8:00 PM\, organized by Digital Hub Monterrey\, and will be held at Matthew restaurant\, near Tecnológico de Monterrey.
LOCATION:TEC | EXPEDITION FEMSA - MATHEW
