SUMMARY:Coffee with Japan: Executive Conversation with SUMITOMO
DESCRIPTION:The panel aims to share how automation and industrial process control strengthen operational efficiency and business competitiveness\, providing SMEs with a clear vision of how to evolve toward more sophisticated industrial standards.  Focusing on automation as an industrial competitiveness strategy. Impact of operational efficiency on quality\, productivity\, and global positioning. Organizational discipline and continuous improvement as the foundation of industrial performance. Opportunities for SMEs to integrate into more technologically advanced value chains. A vision for the future of industrial development in Mexico.\n\nSpeakers: Eugenio José Reyes Guzmán\, Gustavo Rodriguez\, Gustavo Rodríguez
LOCATION:UANL | ESCENARIO SECUNDARIO | (CENTRO DE INTERNACIONALIZACIÓN SALA EMBAJADORES)
