SUMMARY:Coffee UANL with Japan
DESCRIPTION:A unique event where Mexican SMEs connect with the Japanese ecosystem. This special gathering will bring together institutions\, companies\, and key leaders who are strengthening and transforming the relationship between both countries. Participants will take part in activities designed to inspire and foster new opportunities for collaboration.This event is part of the incMTY Festival\, and all participants registered for the Café will receive a discount code to attend the Festival\, which will take place the same day and at the same venue\, allowing attendees to experience both events.The event will take place on Thursday\, March 19\, from 9:00 AM to 5:00 PM at the Centro de Internacionalización\, UANL Ciudad Universitaria.\n\nSpeakers: Eugenio José Reyes Guzmán\, Jose Luis Tobías Osorio \, Mario del Valle
