SUMMARY:Strategy Narrative Lab: The Power of story in business by Fuckup Nights
DESCRIPTION:Strategic Narrative Lab: The Power of Story in Business is an interactive workshop that brings together various contemporary storytelling methodologies used in marketing\, digital content\, technology\, innovation\, and leadership. For two hours\, participants share practical approaches to building stories that resonate with people\, search engines\, and artificial intelligence alike.  The experience connects three dimensions of modern storytelling: (1) narratives for short\, high-impact content\, (2) narratives driven by data and search architecture\, and (3) leadership and learning narratives that can be transformed into memorable TED Talk-style messages. The goal is not to discuss storytelling as an abstract concept\, but to demonstrate how it translates into positioning\, engagement\, authority\, and business growth.\n\nSpeakers: Rubendario Carrero Barroso\, Hazael Misraim L.\, Guillermo Martinez\, Samara Cruz\, Carolina Tovar
LOCATION:UANL | INNOVATION STAGE | (CENTRO DE EDUCACIÓN DIGITAL Y EMPRENDIMIENTO  iOS DEVELOPMENT LAB)
