SUMMARY:COPARMEX Young Entrepreneurs National Meeting – Northeast Region
DESCRIPTION:As part of the INC Monterrey agenda\, COPARMEX National Young Entrepreneurs and COPARMEX Jóvenes Nuevo León will host the Young Entrepreneurs National Meeting – Northeast Region\, a gathering designed for entrepreneurs and business leaders under 35 who are interested in learning about the key topics of the National Commission\, the initiatives driving the Young Entrepreneurs network in Mexico\, and the opportunities for collaboration within the organization.The meeting will feature the participation of a distinguished guest entrepreneur. It will take place at the COPARMEX Nuevo León Business Center.📍 Location: https://maps.app.goo.gl/eDsVaGR2epoB2YhD7Capacity is limited\, so priority will be given to the first attendees to arrive. An ideal space to connect with young entrepreneurs\, share experiences\, and strengthen the region’s young business community.Registration link: https://forms.gle/DMNp5GSTVWkyGN2i9\n\nSpeakers: Empresarios Jóvenes COPARMEX Nacional y  Empresarios Jóvenes COPARMEX Nuevo León
LOCATION:Centro Empresarial COPARMEX NL |  Av. Cuauhtémoc 757\, Barrio Antiguo\, Centro\, 64000 Monterrey\, N.L.
END:VEVENT
