SUMMARY:Thursday Gathering: Shared Horizons: Innovation Mexico-Japan
DESCRIPTION:Venture Café Monterrey Thursday Gathering\, focused on fostering dialogue around the ties between Monterrey and Japan\, as well as exploring opportunities for exchange and business development between both regions.During the event\, we will discuss programs and opportunities with JETRO and JICA\, and introduce the annual Pitch2Tokyo innovation competition by Venture Café Global\, which connects innovators from Venture Café locations around the world.The event will take place on Thursday\, March 19\, from 6:00 to 9:00 PM at Venture Café Monterrey (Expedition FEMSA\, 2nd Floor).\n\nSpeakers: Dan Cabral
LOCATION:TEC | (EXPEDITION FEMSA - VENTURE CAFE)
